{"talk":{"id":66872,"name":"Khulan Batkhuyag: The ancient, earth-friendly wisdom of Mongolian nomads","description":"There's a lot we can learn from Mongolian nomads about how to survive in the years to come, says environmental activist Khulan Batkhuyag. Taking us on a journey through the country's stunning rural landscape, she shows how Mongolian nomads have survived in remote areas for thousands of years by virtue of some truly incredible, earth-friendly, zero-waste innovations. There's wisdom here for all of us on how to live more minimally, sustainably and in harmony with Mother Nature.","slug":"khulan_batkhuyag_the_ancient_earth_friendly_wisdom_of_mongolian_nomads","recorded_at":"2020-09-25 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-09-28 14:55:24","updated_at":"2020-12-24 00:10:17","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":653,"name":"TED@PMI"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/774cb5f0b10307248ea187fedb18b922e0412003_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/774cb5f0b10307248ea187fedb18b922e0412003_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/774cb5f0b10307248ea187fedb18b922e0412003_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/774cb5f0b10307248ea187fedb18b922e0412003_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/489329fed4acd6ca273ab4126c92a51ab018d6bf_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/KhulanBatkhuyag_2020S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5684050,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/KhulanBatkhuyag_2020S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":15746012,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/KhulanBatkhuyag_2020S-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7